        {
            "title": "轟Five Guys「餐廳價錢快餐質素」　鍾培生：食咗交智商稅｜網上熱話(有片)",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"鍾培生炮轟Five Guys「餐廳價錢、快餐質素」，直言食客光顧等同交「智商稅」。(資料圖片)\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/A3981TWoPKWpPJ4LW1syCQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/tl/am730_578/ae811c99a2c1b4435f4b812f5a8950c4\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">鍾培生炮轟Five Guys「餐廳價錢、快餐質素」，直言食客光顧等同交「智商稅」。(資料圖片)</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">有「香港電競之父」之稱的富二代<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-ylk=\"slk:鍾培生;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/鍾培生\">鍾培生</a>，近日在個人社交平台上傳影片，批評美國漢堡品牌<span>Five Guys</span>。他直言該店是用「<span><span><span>餐廳的價錢，食快餐的質素」</span></span></span>，並指<span><span><span>食客光顧等同交「智商稅」</span></span></span>，有關言論引起網民熱議。</p><h2 class=\"mb-module-gap leading-[1.35] text-px22 font-bold lg:text-px24 text-batcave\">直言食<span><span><span><span><span>劣質漢堡</span></span></span></span></span></h2><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span><span><span><span><span>鍾培生在片中</span></span></span></span></span>細數Five Guys的不足。他批評，即使減價後，<span><span><span><span><span>Five Guys一個漢堡連薯條</span></span></span></span></span>仍索價約130元，<span><span><span><span><span>還要標明是內地薯仔，性價比欠奉。他認為Five Guys並非</span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span>快餐價錢，但又無</span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span>快餐的質素。他還說食劣質漢堡，</span></span></span></span></span>卻要由外傭提供服務，<span><span><span><span><span>反問說：「我叫我家外傭做(漢堡)唔好食咩？」</span></span></span></span></span></p><div class=\"bg-card-bg-1 -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-3b24cd83-7b43-3dcc-aff4-0fe0e4baf744-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">鍾培生更將矛頭指向店內策略，直指Five Guys醬料需要額外收費，而其他人<span><span><span>貪吃免費花生。</span></span></span>他總結說：「食Five Guys本身果啲應該係智商稅」，並認為提出這種疑問的人屬低智。</p><h2 class=\"mb-module-gap leading-[1.35] text-px22 font-bold lg:text-px24 text-batcave\">網民： 醬係任選唔駛加錢</h2><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span><span><span><span><span>鍾培生的言論獲得大量網民留言支持，</span></span></span></span></span>有人附和指「連美國人都唔食Five Guys就知佢咩料啦」、「難食，咬落去出水」，建議「食快樂蜂算」。然而，亦有網民指出鍾培生的指控有誤，表示「Five Guys d醬係任選，唔駛加錢」，並質疑「條友食過未架？」，令事件形成兩派爭論。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">根據維基百科，Five Guys是美國連鎖快餐店，以創始人及其四個兒子的名字命名，主打漢堡、熱狗、炸薯條和奶昔，大部分餐廳提供免費花生，內部裝飾以紅白方格瓷磚為特色。公司總部位於維吉尼亞州亞歷山卓，首家餐廳於1986年在維吉尼亞州阿靈頓縣開業，2002年開始加盟連鎖。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文刊登於 AM730 <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:https://www.am730.com.hk/財經/轟five-guys-餐廳價錢快餐質素-鍾培生-食咗交智商稅-網上熱話-有片-/602848?utm_source=yahoorss&amp;utm_medium=referral;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.am730.com.hk/財經/轟five-guys-餐廳價錢快餐質素-鍾培生-食咗交智商稅-網上熱話-有片-/602848?utm_source=yahoorss&amp;utm_medium=referral\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.am730.com.hk/財經/轟five-guys-餐廳價錢快餐質素-鍾培生-食咗交智商稅-網上熱話-有片-/602848?utm_source=yahoorss&amp;utm_medium=referral</a></p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E8%BD%9Ffive-guys-%E9%A4%90%E5%BB%B3%E5%83%B9%E9%8C%A2%E5%BF%AB%E9%A4%90%E8%B3%AA%E7%B4%A0-%E9%8D%BE%E5%9F%B9%E7%94%9F-%E9%A3%9F%E5%92%97%E4%BA%A4%E6%99%BA%E5%95%86%E7%A8%85-074800644.html",
            "pub_date": "2025-09-25 16:35:42",
