            "title": "白宮要求聯邦機構起草政府停擺期間大規模裁員的計畫",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"白宮要求聯邦機構起草政府停擺期間大規模裁員的計畫\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"668\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/xeN9HAdrZJAIKPilZuPEaw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY2ODtjZj13ZWJw/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2025-04/a3c58c00-1d05-11f0-b75f-e15aadfb0917\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">白宮要求聯邦機構起草政府停擺期間大規模裁員的計畫</figcaption></div></figure></div>",
